#: ../../tutorial/run_bfia_job_cn.md:26
msgid "将 AppImage 配置文件应用到 Kuscia 集群中，该配置定义了隐语 ECDH 算法互联互通的镜像和部署模板。配置文件在容器的 `/home/kuscia/scripts/user/bfia/ic-ecdh.yaml`。"
msgstr "Apply the AppImage configuration file to the Kuscia cluster. This configuration defines the image and deployment template for the SecretFlow ECDH algorithm interconnection. The configuration file is located at `/home/kuscia/scripts/user/bfia/ic-ecdh.yaml` within the container."

